              nss←source.⎕NL ¯9.1 ¯9.4 ¯9.5              ⍝ namespaces
         
              No0←~∘0                                    ⍝ Remove fills
              DelRep←'∇'Enclose source.⎕NR               ⍝ ⎕NR with ∇s there
              SaveFn←DelRep Into 2∘Path                  ⍝ Save function there
         
              failed unscripted←No0¨↓⍉↑SaveNs OnEach nss ⍝ go through them
